---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-200 selection:text-blue-900">
<Header />
<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="mb-16">
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-4">
张明昊 <span class="text-slate-400 font-light">| Minghao Zhang</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
清华大学计算机科学与技术系本科生。<br/>
主要研究兴趣包括<strong>机器学习与深度学习</strong>、<strong>多模态大模型</strong>以及<strong>计算机网络安全与体系结构</strong>。
</p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<a href="mailto:zhangmh23@mails.tsinghua.edu.cn" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
Email Me
</a>
<a href="https://github.com/Solaris-celeste" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 bg-white border border-slate-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
GitHub
</a>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Education -->
<section class="mb-16">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
<span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3">
<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222"></path></svg>
</span>
教育背景
</h2>
<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
<div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">清华大学</h3>
<p class="text-slate-500">计算机科学与技术系  本科</p>
</div>
<span class="text-sm text-slate-400 bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">2023 - 至今</span>
</div>
<p class="text-slate-600 mt-3 text-sm">
<strong>GPA:</strong> 3.73 / 4.0 (年级前30%)<br/>
<strong>核心课程:</strong> 软件工程 (A+)、计算机图形学 (A)、计算机网络原理 (A-)、计算机组成原理 (A-)、编译原理 (A-) 等。
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Research & Experience -->
<section class="mb-16">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
<span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3">
<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path></svg>
</span>
科研与实习经历
</h2>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-slate-200">
<div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full -left-[7px] top-1.5 ring-4 ring-slate-50"></div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">计算机系 FIBI Lab 科研实习</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">2025 学年至今</p>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
研究方向包括隐蔽 BGP 劫持的观测与告警、基于表征学习的 BGP 拓扑异常检测等。参与论文 <strong>《Parade: Unified Hyperbolic Representation Learning for High-Fidelity BGP Anomaly Detection》</strong>（学生二作），负责对比实验设计与模型性能测试，已投稿 USENIX Security 2026。
</p>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-slate-200">
<div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-slate-300 rounded-full -left-[7px] top-1.5 ring-4 ring-slate-50"></div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">中科院软件所 实习</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">2025-2026 学年暑期</p>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
参与数据中台后端开发与传染病模型建模与模拟，积累了丰富的工程经验。
</p>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-6 border-l-2 border-slate-200">
<div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-slate-300 rounded-full -left-[7px] top-1.5 ring-4 ring-slate-50"></div>
<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">MoE架构大模型学术新星项目</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">2024-2025 学年</p>
<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
微调金融领域小模型，利用 OpenR1 框架复现 DeepSeek-R1 并评测，参与端侧智能体开发，并基于 Qwen2.5VL 探索无需训练的视觉定位能力提升方法。
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Projects -->
<section class="mb-16">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
<span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 p-2 rounded-lg mr-3">
<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
</span>
项目经历
</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">五级流水线 CPU 设计</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">使用 SystemVerilog 设计支持中断异常与虚拟内存的五级流水线 CPU，负责中断异常与 TLB 设计，项目获满分评级。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">虚拟现实重定向行走系统</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">系统设计与改进，答辩优秀（排名 2/15），获教师表扬。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">MiniDecaf 编译器</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">设计并实现 MiniDecaf 语言编译器，深入理解编译原理与底层架构。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
<h3 class="font-medium text-slate-900 mb-2">GPT 模型训练与微调</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">基于 PyTorch 框架完成 GPT 模型的训练与微调工作。</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
<Footer />
</body>
</html>
